        "bio":"<p>Paul Lewis is Special Projects Editor for the Guardian. He was named Reporter of the Year at the British Press Awards 2010 and won the 2009 <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2009/nov/19/paul-lewis-bevins-prize-g20\">Bevins Prize for outstanding investigative journalism</a>. He previously worked at the Washington Post as the Stern Fellow.<br /><a href=\"mailto:paul.lewis@guardian.co.uk\">paul.lewis@guardian.co.uk</a></p>",
